ReturnPolicy.Description:
Shipping & Refunds
Shop with Confidence, your Satisfaction is Guaranteed

If you're not happy with your purchase, contact us within 14 days of receipt of item and we will issue a refund less shipping and processing fees upon our receipt (10% handling/restocking fee charged)  for returned merchandise. Merchandise must be returned back to us (unworn/unused/unopened & with original tags/factory sealed) within 14 days for refund - return shipping at your own expense. We will not reimburse the return shipping, shipping fees are part of the convenience of online shopping.

Any exchange, credit will be for the original price paid, minus shipping, there will be no 10% handling/restocking fee charged for exchanges, plus shipping if any.

All returns will be processed within 14 days of our receipt in the order they were received. We will email you with notification when the return process has been completed.

Items received for replacement which are unavailable will be refunded or exchanged without a restocking fee. All item measurement charts and specifications are to be used as an "approximation & guideline" only, all our items are brand new first quality.  We are not responsible for any damages incurred during shipping process. 

Thank you for your continued patronage, and please take advantage of our return policy if you are not satisfied with your purchase.
